val parquetFileClick = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypso_kk_dec_data/logs/click/fr/2016/*/*/*.parquet")
val clicksWithoutKFS = parquetFileClick.filter(!($"source".contains("kfs")))
val uniqueUsers = clicksWithoutKFS.select($"userInfo".getItem("userId")).distinct
val uniqueOfferViews = clicksWithoutKFS.select("offerViewId").distinct
val uniqueOfferCategories = clicksWithoutKFS.select("category").distinct
val observedNumberOfRatings = clicksWithoutKFS.groupBy($"userInfo".getItem("userId"),$"offerViewId").count

val numClicks = clicksWithoutKFS.count
val numUsers = uniqueUsers.count
val numOfferViews = uniqueOfferViews.count
val numOfferCategories = uniqueOfferCategories.count
val numInteractions = observedNumberOfRatings.count


val offerId = clicksWithoutKFS.select(substring_index(clicksWithoutKFS("offerViewId"),"-",1))
val uniqueOfferId = offerId.select("substring_index(offerViewId,-,1)").distinct
val numOffers = uniqueOfferId.count

val groupedClicks = clicksWithoutKFS.groupBy($"userInfo".getItem("userId")).count.sort(desc("count"))
val clickAvg = groupedClicks.select(avg($"count"))
clickAvg.show
